<br>
1. The CITY is laid out in four quarters.<br>
2. There are 3 overhead walkways, the North and South ones are short and the EASTERN one is long.<br>
3. All of the &quot; zone/book ports &quot; are on the outer edges, SE, East and NE areas.<br>
4. The DRUID Ring/Circle of Knowledge is at the NW corner of the Northern section or LIBRARY quarter.<br>
5. Two BANKS, one in the SE corner of the LIBRARY (northern area) quarter and there is a Gnome in one of the wooden buildings (forgot to write his name down).<br>
6. Yes, there is a Soulbinder.<br>
<br>
