<br>
You say, 'Hail, Seer Mal Nae`Shi'<br>
<br>
Seer Mal Nae`Shi snaps from her meditation, now aware of your presence.  'Greetings traveler, I am Mal Nae`Shi.  I have come here to heighten my awareness through meditation, much can be learned through a brief exploration of one's self... Assuming there is something there to learn.  While reaching inner peace is a journey each spirit must undertake on its own, I can begin your enlightenment with a short [guided meditation], which will aid your memory, when you are seated and ready.<br>
<br>
You have to be seated when you reply &quot;what guided meditation&quot; for her to tell you the flags.<br>
<br>
If you do not have any flags yet, you will see:<br>
<br>
You manage to recover some images from your childhood, but no recent events spark a memory.<br>
<br>
Otherwise she will list the different flags you have completed<br>
<br>
 <p>Sobasik Desmoosher&lt;BR&gt;<br>
