<br>
 <br>
<br>
He wants Vermiculated armors.  Hand him Vermiculated Armor pieces, and he will reward you with a high end gem (reports are blue diamond, diamond, sapphire).  <br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
One gem per piece of armor.  <br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
A level 61 said that he turned in 4 pieces of armor, and receive 1/4 of a blue in experience also.<br>
