<br>
 <br>
<br>
Guardian Asirav says 'New Tanaan is a haven for knowledge and those who seek it, and exists outside of all normal physical and political boundaries.  If you are [looking] for something, you've come to the right place.  A magically enforced peace exists throughout the city.  No one is able to wield a weapon or cast harmful magic here, making crime almost non-existent.  The city is divided into several sections -- [Kartis], the dark district; [Tanaan], the neutral district; [Selia], the light district; [Jeral] Abbey, the trade plaza; and of course [Myrist], the Great Library.'<br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
You say, 'what looking'<br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
Guardian Asirav says 'Everyone in this city seems to be on a mission of some kind.  I heard recently there are some who are searching for new [armor].  Perhaps you are also looking for something in particular?  If you can't find it at the [bank], then hopefully by using the [portals], you can find what you seek much faster.'<br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
You say, 'what armor'<br>
<br>
 <br>
