<br>
 <br>
<br>
You say, 'what tanaan'<br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
Guardian Asirav says 'Tanaan is the neutral district in the southern part of the city that contains many guild trainers and shops.  Here you will find members of just about any race pursuing their own fields of study in the never-ending quest for knowledge. This area of the city contains portals to Freeport, Qeynos, Ak'Anon, Shar Vahl, Firiona Vie, the Great Divide, and the Nexus.  You can also find the portal to the Plane of Tranquility here as well.'<br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
You say, 'what selia'<br>
<br>
 <br>
<br>
Guardian Asirav says 'Selia is the light district in the eastern part of the city, recognizable by its pristine buildings, relaxing reflecting pools, and lush vegetation.  Many high elves, wood elves, erudites, and halflings come to Selia to meditate or read books they checked out from the Library. The portals to Felwithe, Kelethin, Kaladim, Rivervale, Halas, and Erudin can be found here too.'<br>
<br>
